    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    DiagnosesSystem
    Common interface for all diagnoses and symptoms managers.
    DiagnosesSystemException
    This exception is an unchecked exception, which should be used by all diagnoses systems (classes which implement DiagnosesSystem interface).
    Diagnosis
    Stores diagnosis information.
    DiagnosisCategory
    Stores data about diagnosis category.
    DiagnosisEntity
    Common interface for a diagnosis and a symptom.
    ICD11DiagnosesSystem
    ICD 11-based symptoms and diagnoses management system.
    ICDCodeConverter
    Service interface for classes that convert ICD codes between versions.
    ICDLanguage
    Languages supported by the ICD 11 system.
    ICDVersion
    Enum with known (but not for sure supported) ICD versions.
    Symptom
    Stores symptom information.
    SymptomSupplier
    Service that lists symptoms for a given diagnosis.
    Titled
    Interface for objects that have translatable title.
